  E'You should spend about\n20\nminutes on this task.\nOne of your pen pals will shortly be visiting your city. For some reason, you can not manage to meet him/her at the airport on time.\nWrite a letter asking him/her to wait for you at the airport and tell him/her how to identify you.\nWrite at least\n150\nwords.\nYou do\nNOT\nneed to write any addresses.\nBegin your letter as follows:\nDear .................,',
